snippet.title: Swift: Magical Grid - Hash Map Views Dictionary (Ep 2)
snippet.description:
Today we figure out how to select the cells that are inside of our grid based on the location of our gesture.  First I'll demonstrate a method that isn't all that efficient. Then we take a look at an optimization that uses a HashMap also known as a Dictionary for our cells.  

Enjoy.
